main_body:
Sub-delegation of powers
The Executive Board shall sub-delegate the powers to carry out the following tasks to the member of the Executive Board to whom the Directorate Banknotes reports:
(a) to grant or renew full quality accreditation pursuant to Article 3(4) and Article 7 of Decision ECB/2010/22;
(b) to grant or extend temporary quality accreditation pursuant to Article 4(3) and Article 10 of Decision ECB/2010/22;
(c) to grant or renew environmental accreditation pursuant to Article 6 of Decision ECB/2011/8;
(d) to grant or renew health and safety accreditation pursuant to Article 8 of Decision ECB/2011/8.
